world-110m.geojson — world country polygons for the offline cluster-map basemap.

Source: https://github.com/johan/world.geo.json (countries.geo.json), derived from
Natural Earth 1:110m Cultural Vectors (https://www.naturalearthdata.com/).

Natural Earth is in the PUBLIC DOMAIN — no permission or attribution required
(https://www.naturalearthdata.com/about/terms-of-use/). This NOTICE is courtesy
attribution.

VENDORED, not fetched at runtime from any external host: the file is served
same-origin from apps/web/public/, so rendering the map makes NO external call —
preserving the "web talks only to api-gateway" invariant (spec
docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-09-cluster-workspace-and-location-design.md decision 3).
The map is drawn with Leaflet + L.geoJSON over this basemap and L.circleMarker points,
with NO tileLayer.
